{"word":"Government","slug":"government","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Government</b> Miscellany of minor sub-topics<br/> - Paternal functions of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=57'>Gen 41:57</a> <br/> - Civil service school provided by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=20'>Dan 1:20</a> <br/> - Maintains a system of public instruction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=9'>2Ch 17:9</a> <br/> - Executive departments in<br/> <a href='S:Cabinet'>Cabinet</a>; <a href='S:King'>King</a>; <a href='S:Ruler'>Ruler</a> <br/> - Judicial department in<br/> <a href='S:Court'>Court</a>; <a href='S:Judge'>Judge</a>; <a href='S:Justice'>Justice</a>; <a href='S:Levite'>Levite</a>; <a href='S:Priest'>Priest</a> <br/> Mosaic<br/> - Administrative and Judicial System<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=18&verse=26'>Exo 18:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=17'>Num 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=25'>Num 11:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=17'>Deu 1:17</a> <br/> - Popular, by a national assembly, or its representatives<br/> b Accepted, and agreed to, the law given by Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=8'>Exo 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=3'>Exo 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=7'>Exo 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=15'>Deu 29:15</a><br/> b Refused to make conquest of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=10'>Num 14:10</a><br/> b Chose, or ratified, the chief ruler<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=23'>Num 27:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=24'>1Sa 10:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=22'>1Sa 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=11&verse=15'>1Sa 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=21'>2Sa 3:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=3'>2Sa 5:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=22'>1Ch 29:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=3'>2Ch 23:3</a><br/> b Possessed veto power over the king's purposes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=45'>1Sa 14:45</a><br/> b Possessed veto power over the court in certain capital cases<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=35&verse=12'>Num 35:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=35&verse=25'>Num 35:25</a><br/> - The Delegated, Senatorial Council, closely associated with Moses and subsequent leaders<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=16'>Exo 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=18'>Exo 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=31'>Exo 4:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=21'>Exo 12:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=6'>Exo 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=18&verse=12'>Exo 18:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9&verse=1'>Lev 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=25'>Num 16:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=23'>Deu 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=8'>Exo 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=1'>Exo 24:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?boo